title: Dark Days: Reign of the Vampire
description: The year is 1405 and the deserts of the Eastern world are soaked in blood as the search for the scrolls of Abraith begins. As the time of man comes to pass, a child is born within a clan of slaves, Vor follows his destiny, to protect man knowing he must die and to become the hero he must forsake mankind. To avenge his family he must find redemption.
